The Boy Whose Destiny Was Severed From Him - Acrylic Painting on Canvas

Sometimes we shouldn't be too quick to jump into conclusions. Let's take the time to reflect and observe closely to situations it's gonna help us in the long run if we are careful to observe. Not particularly ourselves but people's lives and situations.
